
h3	match

pre
	<number> = <b>match</b> ( <text>, <pattern> )
	<number> = <b>match</b> ( <text>, <pattern>, <number> )

p
	Test whether the text matches the pattern, which must be a text value too.
p
	Returns	a boolean value: 0 (no) or 1 (yes).
p
	The	optional flag consists of 4	bits:
pre
	1 =	enable backslash escaping
	2 =	directory separators must match	directly
	4 =	initial	dot	in each	file or	directory must match directly
	8 =	compare	case-insensitive



